1
00:01:27,540 --> 00:01:32,660
[Truth or Dare]

2
00:01:32,660 --> 00:01:34,840
[Episode 27]

3
00:01:34,840 --> 00:01:37,180
[Showdown at Mountain Fort]

4
00:02:15,890 --> 00:02:17,670
Father!

5
00:02:23,690 --> 00:02:28,120
Daughter, I'm so sorry.

6
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:30,810
I used all the methods I could think of,

7
00:02:30,810 --> 00:02:33,270
but Young Master Mei said that

8
00:02:33,270 --> 00:02:37,230
he doesn't want to see me and told me to leave.

9
00:02:39,220 --> 00:02:43,240
I also figured that parents can't make decisions for their adult children.

10
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:45,400
I won't implicate you!

11
00:02:46,490 --> 00:02:49,880
Father, let's leave together.

12
00:02:54,310 --> 00:02:56,670
But you and Third Young Master Mei—

13
00:02:57,550 --> 00:02:58,980
Let's go.

14
00:03:16,990 --> 00:03:20,750
Xiao Bao, we'd best leave Qingzhou City as soon as we can.

15
00:03:20,750 --> 00:03:24,180
Otherwise, Nan Batian will trouble us without rest.

16
00:03:24,640 --> 00:03:29,140
The world is so big. Surely there's a place we can make our home.

17
00:03:31,410 --> 00:03:35,620
Then, let's find a place cut off from the world.

18
00:03:35,620 --> 00:03:39,260
I'll give birth to a bunch of little Baozis and little Dumplings for you.

19
00:03:39,790 --> 00:03:45,600
Then... there's no time like the present! Let's do it now!

20
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:52,350
Stop messing around! We still need to inform Third Young Master Mei and Xiao Wanzi.

21
00:03:54,540 --> 00:03:56,010
Let's go.

22
00:03:59,380 --> 00:04:01,300
- Wanzi!
- Speak of the—

23
00:04:05,150 --> 00:04:07,800
Wait. What's wrong, Old He?

24
00:04:08,370 --> 00:04:11,030
Uncle He, did something happen?

25
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:14,290
H-How come you've even started crying?

26
00:04:33,200 --> 00:04:34,980
Wanzi...

27
00:04:37,660 --> 00:04:40,630
Are you really not going to see Third Young Master Mei again?

28
00:04:41,520 --> 00:04:43,850
I don't want

29
00:04:43,850 --> 00:04:47,230
to be the person who he can't even look at without feeling pain.

30
00:05:00,470 --> 00:05:06,280
[Prospering Family]

31
00:05:35,430 --> 00:05:37,730
Isn't it boring to drown your sorrow in alcohol all alone?

32
00:05:37,730 --> 00:05:39,520
I'll keep you company.

33
00:05:42,960 --> 00:05:45,570
I heard about the general situation.

34
00:05:45,570 --> 00:05:47,500
You don't have to.

35
00:05:48,810 --> 00:05:52,070
Look. What use is it to drink here all by yourself?

36
00:05:52,070 --> 00:05:56,750
If you want my opinion, you should just force out the real killer and kill him.

37
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:04,410
These years, I have always been searching for these clues.

38
00:06:05,020 --> 00:06:10,020
All the way till now. Both Crazy Old Chen and the one by the surname of Fan are dead,

39
00:06:10,020 --> 00:06:13,290
but I still haven't found my mother's murderer.

40
00:06:21,290 --> 00:06:25,140
I really regret that that year,

41
00:06:25,620 --> 00:06:30,120
why couldn't I clearly see who the man holding the cane and killing my mother was?

42
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:32,200
The man with a cane?

43
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:37,910
Are you saying the person who killed your mother used a cane?

44
00:06:38,870 --> 00:06:43,150
I remember. I'll remember this for the rest of my life.

45
00:06:44,730 --> 00:06:48,160
The top of it was inlayed with a jewel,

46
00:06:48,160 --> 00:06:52,210
which he ruthlessly smashed onto my mother's body.

47
00:06:54,370 --> 00:06:58,600
Wait! The cane you speak of.

48
00:06:58,600 --> 00:07:00,410
I know it.

49
00:07:01,350 --> 00:07:02,970
You know it?

50
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,620
Who?

51
00:07:08,610 --> 00:07:10,520
Nan Batian.

52
00:07:17,320 --> 00:07:18,970
Nan Batian?

53
00:07:22,090 --> 00:07:24,300
Nan Batian!

54
00:07:25,810 --> 00:07:28,330
I should have figured it out long ago.

55
00:07:28,330 --> 00:07:30,630
Why the man by the name of Fan would hide with the bandits.

56
00:07:30,630 --> 00:07:32,940
He Yizhi gave the information to

57
00:07:32,940 --> 00:07:35,210
Paradise Gambling House.

58
00:07:35,890 --> 00:07:41,170
Then, that Nan Batian brought murderers to assassinate my mother.

59
00:07:41,990 --> 00:07:47,060
Ten years ago, he took the jewel off to conceal it from others.

60
00:07:47,060 --> 00:07:49,930
It's true that very few people know of this.

61
00:07:49,930 --> 00:07:52,080
Nan Batian!

62
00:07:52,660 --> 00:07:55,550
I want your life to be worse than death!

63
00:08:01,700 --> 00:08:04,000
I'll support you.

64
00:08:18,080 --> 00:08:21,140
Now, both Crazy Old Chen and the one named Fan are dead.

65
00:08:21,140 --> 00:08:25,540
Third Young Master Mei will follow the investigation to you soon, Bandit Chief!

66
00:08:27,780 --> 00:08:29,660
What are saying?

67
00:08:30,670 --> 00:08:33,340
Bandit Chief, stop pretending.

68
00:08:33,340 --> 00:08:39,420
I know everything that happened between you and those two 10 years ago.

69
00:08:45,050 --> 00:08:47,060
Now, the Green Dragon Fort's strength is plummeting.

70
00:08:47,060 --> 00:08:49,670
If the Mei family army attacks, I fear you won't even have the time to regret it!

71
00:08:49,670 --> 00:08:51,710
Stop talking!

72
00:08:58,360 --> 00:09:03,820
I am now... already at the end of my resources.

73
00:09:05,660 --> 00:09:08,680
Even if I raise an army right now,

74
00:09:09,610 --> 00:09:12,490
I'm afraid it's already too late.

75
00:09:13,990 --> 00:09:19,410
How about you make a suggestion to me, Brother Situ?

76
00:09:23,630 --> 00:09:26,320
Bandit Chief, don't panic.

77
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:29,570
All you have to do is raise an army.

78
00:09:29,570 --> 00:09:32,490
I will stall the Mei family army.

79
00:09:32,490 --> 00:09:34,960
Stall the Mai family army?

80
00:09:40,450 --> 00:09:42,520
Brother Situ,

81
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:47,190
I didn't know you had such a great ability.

82
00:09:48,380 --> 00:09:51,660
Is there someone powerful backing you? Can you...

83
00:09:59,700 --> 00:10:02,760
introduce him to me?

84
00:10:02,760 --> 00:10:05,070
After you finish recruiting your army

85
00:10:05,070 --> 00:10:11,240
and the crisis subsides, introducing you to him won't be an issue.

86
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:12,780
Good.

87
00:10:17,550 --> 00:10:19,770
- Old Wu!
- Present!

88
00:10:22,550 --> 00:10:23,940
Chief!

89
00:10:23,940 --> 00:10:27,140
Go down the mountain and recruit an army!

90
00:10:27,140 --> 00:10:28,730
Yes!

91
00:10:39,160 --> 00:10:44,360
Xiao Bao, do you really plan on exterminating the bandits alongside the Third Young Master Mei?

92
00:10:45,260 --> 00:10:47,600
Nan Batian is my godfather,

93
00:10:47,600 --> 00:10:50,150
but he has forced me to do bad things ever since my childhood.

94
00:10:50,150 --> 00:10:54,750
I also witnessed how he dealt with disobedient brothers.

95
00:10:54,750 --> 00:10:57,540
Yaoyao, ever since you arrived,

96
00:10:57,540 --> 00:10:59,780
you helped me find out what was correct

97
00:10:59,780 --> 00:11:01,450
and also made me know clearly

98
00:11:01,450 --> 00:11:04,580
that to him, I'm only a tool who was devoted to him.

99
00:11:04,580 --> 00:11:09,680
Once I lose all value to him, he'll just kill me as if I were a dog.

100
00:11:10,490 --> 00:11:14,970
Xiao Bao, I think you're doing the right thing.

101
00:11:14,970 --> 00:11:18,290
Yaoyao, rest assured!

102
00:11:18,290 --> 00:11:22,440
Once I'm done helping the Third Young Master with this matter, I'll take you far away from here.

103
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:24,550
We'll roam all around the world!

104
00:11:24,550 --> 00:11:28,220
As long as I'm with you, I'm fine with going anywhere.

105
00:11:28,900 --> 00:11:30,960
Let's go have a look over there.

106
00:11:32,190 --> 00:11:34,350
- Look, what is that?
- Let's go have a look.

107
00:11:34,350 --> 00:11:37,030
- You haven't paid yet!
- It's only an apple! Who cares?

108
00:11:37,030 --> 00:11:38,780
What are you looking at?

109
00:11:38,780 --> 00:11:42,420
Isn't that Xiao Bao and Boulder-Shattering One?

110
00:11:42,420 --> 00:11:45,270
The road really is narrow for enemies.

111
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:49,450
Young Master, look. They have good products. Let's take one home!

112
00:11:50,290 --> 00:11:51,930
Look!

113
00:11:58,820 --> 00:12:00,800
Master Xiao Bao.

114
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:04,250
Long time no see.

115
00:12:07,660 --> 00:12:10,460
The Green Dragon Fort has already started to recruit an army.

116
00:12:10,460 --> 00:12:12,480
It's not a small manuever.

117
00:12:13,420 --> 00:12:17,750
I considered this before, but I didn't think it would happen so quickly.

118
00:12:17,750 --> 00:12:20,350
What's bound to come will always come.

119
00:12:20,350 --> 00:12:25,080
Young Master, I'll follow you to kill Nan Batian.

120
00:12:25,080 --> 00:12:29,420
The Green Dragon Fort already dominates by sheer force of numbers, and now they're endlessly recruiting an army.

121
00:12:29,420 --> 00:12:31,830
I'm afraid it won't be that easy.

122
00:12:31,830 --> 00:12:36,520
What's there to fear? To catch bandits, first get to their leader. Won't it be over if we go directly for Nan Batian?

123
00:12:36,520 --> 00:12:40,230
Xiao Bao told me that Nan Batian's martial arts are strong.

124
00:12:40,230 --> 00:12:42,520
Even if you and I strike together, we aren't worthy opponents.

125
00:12:42,520 --> 00:12:44,390
Then, what do we do?

126
00:12:46,460 --> 00:12:51,420
In these kinds of circumstances, we must act carefully and cautiously.

127
00:12:51,420 --> 00:12:52,960
A'Rou is right.

128
00:12:52,960 --> 00:12:56,460
We must come up with a completely safe plan.

129
00:12:56,460 --> 00:13:00,330
But now, the only force who can contend with the Green Dragon Fort is the Mei family.

130
00:13:00,330 --> 00:13:04,390
But General Mei, about this, he has always been...

131
00:13:05,560 --> 00:13:08,490
I don't know if this time he will...

132
00:13:08,490 --> 00:13:10,100
I will convince him.

133
00:13:10,100 --> 00:13:14,280
After all, carrying on the family honor from the past decades

134
00:13:14,280 --> 00:13:16,330
has been his lifelong aspiration.

135
00:13:16,330 --> 00:13:18,890
It's also my duty as the younger generation of the Mei family.

136
00:13:18,890 --> 00:13:22,090
Firstly, it's for the commoners of Qingzhou.

137
00:13:22,090 --> 00:13:26,140
This Green Dragon Fort's evil alliance with the Salt Gang

138
00:13:26,140 --> 00:13:28,560
has been robbing the commoners of peaceful days for a long time.

139
00:13:28,560 --> 00:13:34,090
Secondly, it's to avenge my mother.

140
00:13:34,090 --> 00:13:37,490
It's our duty as father and son.

141
00:13:37,490 --> 00:13:40,220
But... even if General Mei agrees,

142
00:13:40,220 --> 00:13:42,480
there's a formation outside of the Green Dragon Fort.

143
00:13:42,480 --> 00:13:45,590
I'm afraid the army won't easily get in.

144
00:13:51,340 --> 00:13:53,060
I will take you to the Green Dragon Fort.

145
00:13:53,060 --> 00:13:55,160
Why are you here?

146
00:13:55,160 --> 00:13:56,520
Where's the princess?

147
00:13:56,520 --> 00:13:59,630
We just bumped into Master Wu.

148
00:13:59,630 --> 00:14:02,820
There were too many of them, and Yingyao was...

149
00:14:03,530 --> 00:14:04,850
was abducted.

150
00:14:04,850 --> 00:14:06,460
What?

151
00:14:12,180 --> 00:14:16,290
Then let's entrust Master Xiao Bao with going to the Green Dragon Fort.

152
00:14:16,290 --> 00:14:18,530
We'll split our troops two ways for now.

153
00:14:18,530 --> 00:14:21,330
I will ask Father to dispatch the troops.

154
00:14:21,330 --> 00:14:23,990
Siheng, go with Master Xiao Bao

155
00:14:23,990 --> 00:14:26,290
and scout the road to Green Dragon Fort first.

156
00:14:27,120 --> 00:14:28,730
Yes.

157
00:14:31,690 --> 00:14:35,790
A'Rou, Xiao Wanzi and He Yizhi will be left in your care.

158
00:14:35,790 --> 00:14:39,420
Yes. Rest assured, Young Master.

159
00:14:39,420 --> 00:14:41,860
Make her wait for my return.

160
00:14:48,300 --> 00:14:50,790
So, Brother Situ,

161
00:14:50,790 --> 00:14:53,240
I'm almost done with recruiting the army.

162
00:14:53,240 --> 00:14:57,500
You said you could stall the Mei family army. Are you sure?

163
00:14:58,190 --> 00:14:59,630
Rest assured.

164
00:14:59,630 --> 00:15:02,740
The Mei family army will definitely leave.

165
00:15:03,360 --> 00:15:07,760
By then, Qingzhou City will belong to your Green Dragon Fort.

166
00:15:07,760 --> 00:15:08,830
Great!

167
00:15:08,830 --> 00:15:13,110
Chief! I'm done recruiting the army.

168
00:15:13,110 --> 00:15:16,020
In addition, I brought someone back for you.

169
00:15:18,930 --> 00:15:21,010
Move! Move!

170
00:15:24,620 --> 00:15:27,990
Xiao Wanzi! You slut!

171
00:15:27,990 --> 00:15:31,460
You hurt me really badly.

172
00:15:31,460 --> 00:15:33,170
Heaven has assisted me.

173
00:15:33,170 --> 00:15:36,720
Once I take down Qingzhou City, I will marry you!

174
00:15:36,720 --> 00:15:39,290
I'll have you suffer worse than death!

175
00:15:39,290 --> 00:15:40,940
I won't marry you even if I must die!

176
00:15:40,940 --> 00:15:42,940
It's not up to you anymore.

177
00:15:42,940 --> 00:15:44,200
Take her away!

178
00:15:44,200 --> 00:15:46,090
Wait!

179
00:15:57,070 --> 00:16:00,700
This is an ornament of the imperial family.

180
00:16:00,700 --> 00:16:02,840
How come you have it?

181
00:16:03,460 --> 00:16:05,860
Someone gave it to me. Isn't that acceptable?

182
00:16:05,860 --> 00:16:10,100
Brother Situ, she's merely a girl performing on the streets.

183
00:16:10,100 --> 00:16:11,890
Where would she get an ornament of the imperial family?

184
00:16:11,890 --> 00:16:14,860
There's no need to make a fuss about nothing. Come!

185
00:16:17,310 --> 00:16:20,630
- Let's go!
- Move!

186
00:16:39,570 --> 00:16:41,730
From now on, let's just forget about Your Highness and such.

187
00:16:41,730 --> 00:16:43,760
-  Just call me Xiao—
- Princess!

188
00:16:46,390 --> 00:16:50,720
- Eldest Brother Situ, in the future, how about I learn business from you?
- Nonsense!

189
00:16:50,720 --> 00:16:53,330
What nonsense? I seriously want to learn!

190
00:16:53,330 --> 00:16:54,500
You are a princess!

191
00:16:54,500 --> 00:16:56,270
So what if I am a princess?

192
00:16:56,270 --> 00:16:59,690
From childhood, I've always known that it's best to rely on myself!

193
00:16:59,690 --> 00:17:01,660
I insist on learning.

194
00:17:07,550 --> 00:17:10,620
[General Mei - Yongzhou's in a dire situation in the war. You are ordered to bring your troops to the rescue.]

195
00:17:17,310 --> 00:17:18,250
Father.

196
00:17:18,250 --> 00:17:20,910
Your eyes have just recovered. You should rest more.

197
00:17:20,910 --> 00:17:23,320
It's no longer serious. I just need to ask you to send out the troops.

198
00:17:23,320 --> 00:17:24,930
Send out troops?

199
00:17:24,930 --> 00:17:28,030
Is it because of Green Dragon Fort?

200
00:17:28,030 --> 00:17:31,790
I got a tip that the Green Dragon Fort has been recruiting an army lately.

201
00:17:31,790 --> 00:17:34,140
They will be attacking Qingzhou soon.

202
00:17:34,980 --> 00:17:39,350
These bandits. They're getting bolder and bolder.

203
00:17:39,350 --> 00:17:42,610
Father, every day that the Green Dragon Fort doesn't come out,

204
00:17:42,610 --> 00:17:45,860
is a day that the commoners of Qingzhou will not be able to have peace.

205
00:17:45,860 --> 00:17:49,760
Moreover, I discovered that Nan Batian

206
00:17:49,760 --> 00:17:51,960
is my mother's murderer.

207
00:17:51,960 --> 00:17:54,040
Li Tianlong was the one who put him up to it.

208
00:17:54,040 --> 00:17:55,790
What?

209
00:17:58,230 --> 00:18:02,440
Nan Batian? It was him!

210
00:18:02,440 --> 00:18:05,300
I will tear you into a million shreds!

211
00:18:06,440 --> 00:18:09,310
Since we've already found the killer,

212
00:18:09,310 --> 00:18:15,570
Father, with respect to love and logic, we must fight this battle no matter what!

213
00:18:16,520 --> 00:18:18,370
Shiqing.

214
00:18:19,420 --> 00:18:21,210
Look.

215
00:18:24,530 --> 00:18:25,630
This—

216
00:18:25,630 --> 00:18:28,630
Yongzhou's in a dire situation in their war. The court has ordered me

217
00:18:28,630 --> 00:18:32,630
to bring all of our troops to rescue Yongzhou.

218
00:18:32,630 --> 00:18:35,580
- When will you depart?
- Tomorrow morning.

219
00:18:36,960 --> 00:18:40,320
In the Yongzhou war, our military strength gives us an advantage.

220
00:18:40,320 --> 00:18:42,590
There hasn't been a request to increase military strength.

221
00:18:42,590 --> 00:18:44,820
Why would they suddenly dispatch the Mei family army?

222
00:18:44,820 --> 00:18:49,320
This matter truly is somewhat suspicious.

223
00:18:50,320 --> 00:18:55,030
The Green Dragon Fort is recruiting an army while the imperial court suddenly dispatches the Mei family army.

224
00:18:55,030 --> 00:18:58,990
Father, I think this isn't as simple as a coincidence.

225
00:18:58,990 --> 00:19:03,440
Father, we can't delay wiping out the Green Dragon Fort. I will go immediately.

226
00:19:03,440 --> 00:19:05,000
No.

227
00:19:05,000 --> 00:19:08,530
Shiqing, that Nan Batian is cruel and merciless. He has many people and lots of power.

228
00:19:08,530 --> 00:19:10,850
If anything happens to you,

229
00:19:10,850 --> 00:19:14,270
where would I have the self-respect to meet the Mei family's ancestors?

230
00:19:14,270 --> 00:19:19,000
But, Father, the Qingzhou commoners are all our family!

231
00:19:19,000 --> 00:19:22,620
Shiqing, without the Mei family army, how could you combat him?

232
00:19:22,620 --> 00:19:26,660
Father, rest assured. The people of Ruyi Restaurant are all loyal to me.

233
00:19:26,660 --> 00:19:30,010
We will pledge our lives to protect Qingzhou.

234
00:19:43,480 --> 00:19:46,300
Lady A'Rou, why are you here?

235
00:19:48,500 --> 00:19:50,340
Let's talk inside.

236
00:19:53,050 --> 00:19:55,200
Lady A'Rou, what has exactly happened?

237
00:19:55,200 --> 00:19:56,850
It is no longer safe here.

238
00:19:56,850 --> 00:19:59,080
I'm going to take you specifically to a temple in the west of the city to lay low.

239
00:19:59,080 --> 00:20:00,540
Did something happen to Shiqing?

240
00:20:00,540 --> 00:20:04,700
No. Nan Batian is going to concentrate his forces on attacking Qingzhou City.

241
00:20:04,700 --> 00:20:08,520
Young Master and the others are going to surround the fort, and...

242
00:20:08,520 --> 00:20:11,040
And what?

243
00:20:11,040 --> 00:20:15,450
The young master already knows that Nan Batian is his nemesis who murdered his mother.

244
00:20:17,410 --> 00:20:19,640
This battle is not small.

245
00:20:19,640 --> 00:20:23,710
Young Master asked me to help you and Uncle settle down.

246
00:20:23,710 --> 00:20:27,360
Then, where is he now? Is Shiqing already going to the fort?

247
00:20:27,360 --> 00:20:29,600
Lady A'Rou, will you please tell me?

248
00:20:29,600 --> 00:20:32,280
I know you really want to go and help,

249
00:20:32,280 --> 00:20:36,130
but Young Master specifically requested that you rest assured and wait for his return.

250
00:20:36,140 --> 00:20:39,390
I have the martial arts to defend myself. I won't cause trouble.

251
00:20:39,390 --> 00:20:44,180
