253
00:20:52,110 --> 00:20:54,840
Lady A'Rou! I, He Yizhi, have said

254
00:20:54,840 --> 00:20:57,160
that even if I must work like a horse, I will atone for my sin!

255
00:20:57,160 --> 00:20:59,980
This time, I definitely cannot run away again. Right, Daughter?

256
00:20:59,980 --> 00:21:03,070
Lady, A'Rou, just tell us.

257
00:21:05,080 --> 00:21:08,040
All right. Follow me.

258
00:21:11,310 --> 00:21:13,300
Brothers!

259
00:21:13,300 --> 00:21:16,570
Today, our mountain fort has been added to.

260
00:21:16,570 --> 00:21:19,390
Many new faces have arrived.

261
00:21:20,240 --> 00:21:22,640
As long as you work properly with me,

262
00:21:22,640 --> 00:21:25,230
I will promise you will be greatly rewarded.

263
00:21:25,230 --> 00:21:28,650
Good!

264
00:21:28,650 --> 00:21:33,860
In the past, we stayed here without daring to leave.

265
00:21:33,860 --> 00:21:36,010
In the future, we will no longer tolerate this useless energy!

266
00:21:36,010 --> 00:21:38,810
I have already received reliable information.

267
00:21:38,820 --> 00:21:42,690
The Mei family army has gone to Yongzhou to battle!

268
00:21:42,700 --> 00:21:44,230
Come, Brothers!

269
00:21:44,230 --> 00:21:46,540
Drink this cup of wine.

270
00:21:46,540 --> 00:21:48,820
We will conquer Qingzhou City.

271
00:21:48,820 --> 00:21:50,940
Cheers!

272
00:21:57,570 --> 00:21:59,020
Nan Xiang.

273
00:21:59,640 --> 00:22:02,160
Nan Xiang, come.

274
00:22:02,160 --> 00:22:04,520
Drink with everyone.

275
00:22:04,520 --> 00:22:06,070
Quickly!

276
00:22:09,460 --> 00:22:12,750
- Boss's daughter is really pretty, right?
- Yes.

277
00:22:12,750 --> 00:22:14,710
In the future, whoever marries her

278
00:22:14,710 --> 00:22:17,270
will be the next bandit chief!

279
00:22:17,950 --> 00:22:21,220
As long as you have major achievements in battle,

280
00:22:21,220 --> 00:22:24,660
it won't be impossible to marry my daughter!

281
00:22:24,660 --> 00:22:26,650
