- Yes!

282
00:22:26,650 --> 00:22:28,410
Father! You...

283
00:22:28,410 --> 00:22:30,660
Good! Good!

284
00:22:33,080 --> 00:22:35,710
She's mad.

285
00:22:35,710 --> 00:22:38,020
- She got bashful.
- Thin-skinned.

286
00:22:38,830 --> 00:22:40,820
Young ladies

287
00:22:40,820 --> 00:22:43,220
are easily affronted. Drink!

288
00:22:43,220 --> 00:22:47,540
Yes! Drink! Come on!

289
00:22:47,540 --> 00:22:50,430
- Old Wu.
- Chief.

290
00:22:51,090 --> 00:22:53,240
Take care of the brothers.

291
00:22:53,240 --> 00:22:56,740
Eat well, but don't drink too much. We still have huge things to do.

292
00:22:56,740 --> 00:22:58,520
Understood.

293
00:23:00,710 --> 00:23:02,870
Brothers, drink however you'd like!

294
00:23:19,550 --> 00:23:22,850
Stop! What are you intending to do?

295
00:23:22,850 --> 00:23:23,900
I want to go down the mountain.

296
00:23:23,900 --> 00:23:25,870
Down the mountain?

297
00:23:26,480 --> 00:23:27,650
Why are you going down the mountain?

298
00:23:27,650 --> 00:23:29,540
You know!

299
00:23:30,530 --> 00:23:33,650
Are you going behind your father's back

300
00:23:33,650 --> 00:23:36,450
