301
00:23:36,450 --> 00:23:38,740
No.

302
00:23:38,740 --> 00:23:42,380
Father, I always thought I was the daughter you cherished most.

303
00:23:42,380 --> 00:23:46,950
But what was the result? I'm just the tool you use to keep your subordinates in check!

304
00:23:46,950 --> 00:23:51,310
Honestly, I'm not stupid. I always knew you were using Xiao Bao.

305
00:23:51,310 --> 00:23:54,800
