306
00:24:08,720 --> 00:24:13,230
Looks like I've spoiled you too much.

307
00:24:13,230 --> 00:24:18,320
I'm telling you. If you dare to step through this doorframe today,

308
00:24:18,320 --> 00:24:20,860
I will break your legs.

309
00:24:22,690 --> 00:24:26,970
